    (spawn (rippler 2 3))
    (spawn (rippler 3 0))
    (spawn (rippler 3 1))
    (spawn (rippler 3 2))
    (spawn (rippler 3 3))))
```

[VISUAL: A 4×4 grid of circles, each hopping upward in a radial wave expanding from the center.]

