### Circle around a point

Eight entities orbiting a center, each offset by 45°.

```scheme
(motion
  (define (orbiter idx total)
    (sprite
      (shape 'circle 12)
      (color 0.4 0.6 0.5 1.0)
      (route
        (let* ((angle (* idx (/ 6.28318 total)))
               (radius 120)
               (cx 300)
               (cy 250)
               (x0 (+ cx (* radius (cos angle))))
               (y0 (+ cy (* radius (sin angle)))))
          (from (xy x0 y0))
          (loop
            (arc cx cy radius angle (+ angle 6.28318) 4.0 'ease-in-out)
            (set! angle (+ angle 6.28318)))))))
  
  (world
    (spawn (orbiter 0 8))
    (spawn (orbiter 1 8))
    (spawn (orbiter 2 8))
    (spawn (orbiter 3 8))
    (spawn (orbiter 4 8))
    (spawn (orbiter 5 8))
    (spawn (orbiter 6 8))
    (spawn (orbiter 7 8))))
```

